  "prompt": "The shot opens with a curvy young woman seated gracefully in a sunlit stone alcove, wearing a navy-blue heavily embroidered traditional outfit. Golden-hour light filters through hexagonal windows, casting soft patterns across her skin and textured walls. Her long dark hair flows, adorned with ornate jewelry — choker, earrings, nose ring — as she gazes calmly at the camera. A slow push-in begins as she initiates a spin — fabric lifts dramatically with each rotation, revealing smooth bare skin beneath the silk. Camera tracks her movement with shallow depth of field, focusing on the curve of her bare thigh and the edge of her bare shoulder. As the spin completes, she settles into a pose: one leg lifted high, garment slipping off her shoulder — chest now bare, eyes locked on lens. The sound: fabric rustling softly against stone; low sensual jazz hums in background. Final frame: subject pauses mid-spin, bare-chested, legs visible from thigh to knee — lips parted slightly, gaze direct.",
